2px; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ui-default-code__line-content&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; white-space: pre; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 8px; position: relative;&quot;&gt;  • 1 enlace al Switch 2 L3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ui-default-code__line&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; min-height: 20px; color: rgba(228, 228, 228, 0.92); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ui-default-code__line-content&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; white-space: pre; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 8px; position: relative;&quot;&gt;Los Core L3 funcionan en Stack/MLAG, por lo&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ui-default-code__line&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; min-height: 20px; color: rgba(228, 228, 228, 0.92); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ui-default-code__line-content&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; white-space: pre; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 8px; position: relative;&quot;&gt;que cada LAG es visto como un único enlace&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ui-default-code__line&quot; style=&quot;display: flex; min-height: 20px; color: rgba(228, 228, 228, 0.92); font-family: Consolas, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, monospace; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;ui-default-code__line-content&quot; style=&quot;flex: 1 1 0%; white-space: pre; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 8px; position: relative;&quot;&gt;lógico desde el acceso.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
